content_segments.text: **Important:** RF (stainless steel) is **not available** for GDMI. Available material options: Aluzink, Zinkmagnesium. Please select an available material to proceed.

This GDMI filter housing is for an outdoor data center intake. Unfortunately, the GDMI family is not rated for outdoor installation due to its bolted construction, which does not meet the leakage class and hygiene requirements for outdoor environments. This configuration is therefore blocked.

Additionally, the intended installation environment exposes the system to high humidity and outdoor condensation. High humidity can accelerate zinc corrosion, potentially reducing the service life of the housing. Outdoor condensation can cause condensation on non-insulated metal surfaces.
I also need two more details to finalize the configuration:
What is the desired airflow for the GDMI filter housing?
